---

<PageLayout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
>
  
  <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 mt-4">
    <Breadcrumbs 
      items={[
        { name: "Home", url: "/" },
        { name: "Service Areas", url: "/service-areas" },
        { name: "Pickering" }
      ]}
    />
  </div>

<!-- Location Hero -->
  <Hero 
    title="Moisture Protection Pickering"
    subtitle="Professional basement protection and foundation repair serving all local neighborhoods. 25-year warranty, free inspection."
    primaryCTA={{ text: "Get Free Quote", href: "/free-inspection" }}
    secondaryCTA={{ text: "Call: 437-545-0067", href: "tel:437-545-0067" }}
    backgroundImage="/images/dryspace_hero_desktop.webp"
    badge="Serving the Area"
  />

  <!-- Internal Links -->
  <section class="py-8 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <InternalLinks category="location" currentPage="pickering" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats -->
  <Stats />

  <!-- Local Information Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">MOISTURE PROTECTION SERVICES LOCALLY</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg  max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
            The area presents unique moisture challenges combining conservation area restrictions with diverse property types from rural estates to urban subdivisions. Located within the Rouge River watershed and adjacent to sensitive environmental areas, basement protection requires specialized knowledge of conservation compliance and mixed development patterns.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">LOCAL QUICK FACTS</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 ">
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Population</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">101,000</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Average Home Age</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">20-40 YEARS MIXED</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Annual Rainfall</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">840MM + CONSERVATION</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Frost Line</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">1.2 METERS</span>
              </li>
                <li class="flex justify-between items-center pb-2 border-b border-slate-100">
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-600 uppercase">Flood Risk</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">ROUGE RIVER SEASONAL</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-navy-900 border-2 border-slate-200  p-6">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 uppercase">WHY THE AREA NEEDS MOISTURE PROTECTION</h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Conservation area glacial deposits vary widely</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Rouge River watershed affects groundwater</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Conservation areas retain more moisture</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Freeze-thaw cycles damage foundations</span>
              </li>
                <li class="text-sm text-slate-300 flex items-start">
                <span class="mr-2 text-cyan-400">•</span>
                <span>Rouge River and wetland seasonal flooding</span>
              </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Neighborhoods We Serve</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our local moisture protection team serves all neighborhoods including:
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {["Bay Ridges","Rouge Park","Liverpool","Dunbarton","Claremont","Brougham"].map((neighborhood) => (
              <span class="border-2 border-slate-200 px-4 py-2 text-sm">
                {neighborhood}
              </span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <Services />

  <!-- Location Features -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">WHY CHOOSE DRYSPACE LOCALLY</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Local expertise combined with industry-leading warranties and service
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Highlighted Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-amber-500 border-2 border-slate-700 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-900">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      
      <!-- Regular Features -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {locationFeatures.filter(f => !f.highlight).map((feature) => (
          <div class="bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 p-6 hover:border-slate-300 transition-colors">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 uppercase">{feature.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <Process />


  <!-- Location Image Showcase -->
  <LocationImageShowcase city="Pickering" />

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <Testimonials />

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">LOCAL MOISTURE PROTECTION FAQS</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Common questions from local homeowners</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        {locationFAQs.map((faq, index) => (
          <details class="mb-4 border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase pr-4">{faq.question}</h3>
                <span class="text-slate-400 flex-shrink-0 text-2xl">+</span>
              </div>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
              <p class="text-slate-600">{faq.answer}</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-navy-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase">PROTECT YOUR CONSERVATION AREA PROPERTY</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Environmental-compliant moisture protection for the area's diverse urban and rural properties
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="/free-inspection"
            class="bg-amber-500 text-black px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-amber-400 transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Get Conservation Area Assessment
          </a>
          <a 
            href="tel:437-545-0067"
            class="border-2 border-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-colors uppercase"
          >
            Call: 437-545-0067
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center text-cyan-400">
          <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase">24/7 Emergency Service Available</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(localBusinessSchema)}>
<BreadcrumbSchema items={[{name: 'Home', url: '/'}, {name: 'Locations', url: '/locations'}, {name: 'Pickering'}]} />
